title: Fibre Containers
additional-note: The first and only book or contribution copyright renewal associated with this serial is a 1967 renewal for 'The manufacture of paperboard' by Norbert Rennicke, which the record says was published serially in Fibre Containers, 'Oct. 1938 - Oct. 1939'.  This renewal would likely be too late for installments published in 1938, but might cover installments published in 1939.  We do not know the date of the first installment published in 1939.
